data.text: @chuerta1 @POTUS @VP @CDCDirector @NationalGuard @KateBrownForOR i drove 5 miles east to the rural fire department, drove right in, filled out paperwork, got jabbed, drove out. easy peasy

@econklin4 @POTUS @VP @CDCDirector @NationalGuard @KateBrownForOR Pfizer. I couldn't complain about the process. They're calling it all4oregonvaccine and it was very well coordinated.
